OL,3,CDad went on the run with teenage son
OL,4,Cafter stabbing wife in 'ferocious'
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA dad who went on the run with his
OL,8,Fteenage son after stabbing his wife
OL,9,Fmultiple times in a "ferocious attack"
OL,10,Fand locking her in the family home has
OL,11,Fbeen jailed.
OL,13,FMark Taylor, of Wheatlands Lane,
OL,14,FBaslow, Derbyshire denied the offence
OL,15,Fbut was found guilty on Tuesday 15
OL,16,FAugust after a trial at Derby Crown
OL,17,FCourt.
