OL,3,CDad went on the run with teenage son
OL,4,Cafter stabbing wife in 'ferocious'
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHe appeared at the same court on
OL,8,FMonday 14 October for sentence, when
OL,9,Fhe was jailed for 23 years with a five-
OL,10,Fyear extension for dangerousness.
OL,12,FHe was also handed an indefinite
OL,13,Frestraining order preventing him from
OL,14,Fhaving any contact with his wife and
OL,15,Fson.
OL,17,FTaylor attacked his wife on Thursday
OL,18,F15 February, in what detectives
OL,19,Fdescribed as a "ferocious and
OL,20,Fsustained attack".
