OL,3,CDad went on the run with teenage son
OL,4,Cafter stabbing wife in 'ferocious'
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe 57-year-old stabbed his wife so
OL,8,Fhard that the knife he used snapped.
OL,9,FHe continued to assault his wife,
OL,10,Fgrabbing a second knife.
OL,12,FHe then demanded she handed over her
OL,13,Fphone to him saying he would call an
OL,14,Fambulance.
OL,16,FInstead, Taylor said "this will be the
OL,17,Fend of you" before locking the doors
OL,18,Fto their house in Baslow and driving
OL,19,Faway with the couple's son.
