OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FTaylor's wife tried to call for help
OL,8,Fthrough the letterbox before managing
OL,9,Fto crawl up the stairs where she
OL,10,Fshouted out of a bedroom window and
OL,11,Fmanaged to catch the attention of a
OL,12,Fpassing dog walker who called
OL,13,Femergency services.
OL,15,FShe was taken to hospital for
OL,16,Ftreatment after suffering stab wounds
OL,17,Fto her neck, arm, chest and stomach in
OL,18,Fthe February 15 attack.
