OL,7,FAutomatic number plate recognition
OL,8,Fcameras captured Taylor's car moving
OL,9,Faround Derbyshire before heading to
OL,10,FCheshire.
OL,12,FHe was stopped later that day by
OL,13,FCheshire Police and arrested,
OL,14,Fsubsequently being charged with
OL,15,Fattempted murder.
