OL,7,FDerbyshire Police Temporary Detective
OL,8,FConstable Amber Holmes, who led the
OL,9,Finvestigation, said: "This was a
OL,10,Fferocious and sustained attack by
OL,11,FTaylor on his wife who genuinely
OL,12,Ffeared she was going to die.
OL,14,FAfter this incident she disclosed to
OL,15,Fpolice that she had been suffering
OL,16,Ffrom domestic abuse at the hands of
OL,17,Fher husband for around 40 years
OL,18,Fincluding a previous incident
OL,19,Finvolving a knife.
