OL,7,F"It's clear from the history and the
OL,8,Factions of Taylor on this day that he
OL,9,Fposed a very real threat to his wife.
OL,11,F"I am pleased therefore that the judge
OL,12,Fhas recognised the danger posed by
OL,13,FTaylor with this extended sentence."
